         <abstract>
            <p>Incorporating several new adjustments in their procedure, the authors estimate the 1974 income statement effects of general price-level adjustments for the 30 Dow Jones companies, 44 other large corporations and the 24 public utilities in the Dow Jones and Standard and Poor's public utilities indexes.</p>
